%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22EXCLUSIVE%3A%20Elon%20Musk%20filed%20custody%20suit%20against%20Grimes%20first%2C%20asking%20for%20'relationship'%20with%20his%20children%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20with%20three-year-old%20child%20X%20on%20his%20shoulders%20next%20to%20Hungarian%20President%20Katalin%20Novak.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651f4fcd6e038039826b0670%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20this%20picture%20issued%20Sept.%2026%2C%202023%2C%20by%20the%20Hungarian%20President's%20Press%20Office%2C%20Hungarian%20President%20Katalin%20Novak%20and%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Tesla%2C%20Inc.%20Elon%20Musk%20tours%20the%20recently%20inaugurated%20Tesla%20plant%20Gigafactory%20Texas%20in%20Austin%2C%20Texas%2C%20Monday%2C%20Sept.%2025%2C%202023.%20Novak%20stays%20on%20a%20week-long%20visit%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20%3Cp%3E(Gyula%20Bartos%2FHungarian%20President's%20Press%20Office%2FMTI%20via%20AP)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGrimes%20filed%20a%20custody%20suit%20against%20Elon%20Musk%20in%20San%20Francisco%20late%20last%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20Insider%20learned%20Musk%20sued%20Grimes%20first%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Bestablish%20the%20parent-child%20relationship%26quot%3B%20with%20his%20kids.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20claims%20she%20moved%20to%20California%20%26quot%3Bin%20an%20apparent%20attempt%20to%20circumvent%20jurisdiction%26quot%3B%20of%20Texas%20courts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHeadlines%20around%20the%20world%20announced%20this%20week%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-grimes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EGrimes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20sued%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20custody%20of%20their%20three%20children%2C%20but%20it%20was%20Musk%20himself%20who%20first%20quietly%20sued%20Grimes%20last%20month%2C%20Insider%20has%20learned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20September%207%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3ETesla%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20CEO%20sued%20his%20sometimes-girlfriend%20Grimes%20to%20establish%20a%20relationship%20and%20access%20to%20his%20children%20and%20accused%20her%20of%20moving%20to%20California%20to%20escape%20the%20reach%20of%20Texas%20courts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24016602-elon-musk-grimes-texas-petition-to-adjudicate-parentage-redacted%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Efilings%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eobtained%20by%20Insider%2C%20Musk%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Bestablish%20the%20parent-child%20relationship%26quot%3B%20with%20his%20and%20Grimes'%20children%20X%2C%20who%20is%203%2C%20and%20one-year-olds%20Exa%20(or%20Y)%20and%20Tau.%20He%20said%20Grimes%2C%20whose%20real%20name%20is%20Claire%20Boucher%2C%20lived%20with%20him%20and%20their%20children%20from%20May%20to%20July%20of%20this%20year.%20He%20also%20claimed%20she%20moved%20to%20California%20%26quot%3Bin%20an%20apparent%20attempt%20to%20circumvent%20jurisdiction%26quot%3B%20of%20Texas%20courts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMusk%20said%2C%20in%20the%20filings%2C%20he%20believed%20the%20custody%20dispute%20would%20settle%2C%20but%20wanted%20Texas%20courts%20to%20weigh%20in%20if%20it%20didn't.%20His%20case%20was%20served%20to%20Grimes%20on%20September%2013%2C%20and%20she%20filed%20her%20own%20suit%20against%20Musk%20on%20September%2029.%20Grimes'%20lawsuit%20is%20requesting%20physical%20custody%20of%20the%20children%20and%20includes%20a%20%26quot%3Bstandard%20restraining%20order%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20prevent%20the%20children%20from%20being%20moved%20out%20of%20California%20by%20either%20parent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMusk%20asserted%20that%20disclosing%20information%20about%20the%20case%20%26quot%3Bwould%20jeopardize%20the%20health%2C%20safety%20or%20liberty%26quot%3B%20of%20himself%2C%20Grimes%2C%20and%20their%20children.%20The%20case%20would%20be%20hard%20for%20an%20outsider%20to%20find%3B%20the%20children's%20names%20weren't%20used%2C%20Musk%20was%20identified%20only%20by%20his%20middle%20initial%2C%20%26quot%3BR.%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Grimes%20by%20hers%2C%20%26quot%3BE.%26quot%3B%20A%20hearing%20was%20originally%20set%20for%20Friday%2C%20but%20it%20was%20canceled%20after%20the%20parties%20agreed%20to%20a%20seal%2C%20according%20to%20a%20court%20official.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELawyers%20for%20Musk%20and%20Grimes%20declined%20to%20comment%20and%20Musk%20didn't%20respond%20to%20efforts%20to%20reach%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EMusk%20and%20Grimes%20have%20had%20a%20contentious%20relationship%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20just%20the%20latest%20dust-up%20over%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-children%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EMusk%20children%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20between%20Musk%20and%20Grimes%2C%20the%20musician%20with%20whom%20he's%20been%20in%20an%20on-again%2C%20off-again%20relationship%20since%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrimes'%20younger%20two%20children%20with%20Musk%20have%20mostly%20avoided%20the%20limelight.%20But%20her%20eldest%20son%2C%20X%2C%20has%20become%20a%20common%20figure%20in%20Musk's%20orbit.%20The%20three-year-old%20has%20attended%20live%20interviews%20with%20Musk%2C%20met%20with%20international%20leaders%2C%20and%20attended%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESpaceX%20rocket%20launches%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20Grimes%20has%20said%20she'd%20prefer%20to%20keep%20her%20children%20out%20of%20the%20public%20eye.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20is%20going%20on%20with%20family%20stuff%2C%20I%20just%20feel%20like%20kids%20need%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20it%2C%20and%20X%20is%20just%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Vanity%20Fair%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20I%20think%20E%20is%20really%20seeing%20him%20as%20a%20prot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%20and%20bringing%20him%20to%20everything%20and%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20couple%20first%20broke%20up%20in%202021%2C%20until%20recently%20their%20relationship%20has%20appeared%20cordial.%20Grimes%20even%20continued%20to%20live%20with%20Musk%20in%20Austin%20for%20a%20period%20after%20they%20first%20broke%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20singer%20appeared%20to%20reference%20a%20legal%20issue%20with%20Musk%20in%20a%20post%20she%20quickly%20wrote%20and%20then%20deleted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BTell%20Elon%20to%20let%20me%20see%20my%20son%20or%20plz%20respond%20to%20my%20lawyer%2C%26quot%3B%20Grimes%20wrote%20in%20the%20since-deleted%20September%207%20post.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrimes%20posted%20on%20X%20in%20response%20to%20a%20photo%20of%20Musk%20alongside%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-shivon-zilis-secret-twins-neuralink-tesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EShivon%20Zilis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20another%20one%20of%20the%20women%20he%20has%20fathered%20children%20with.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMusk%20has%2010%20known%20living%20children%20with%20three%20different%20women.%20In%20a%20biography%20on%20Musk%2C%20Walter%20Isaacson%20wrote%20that%20the%20billionaire%20kept%20his%20decision%20to%20father%20a%20child%20with%20Zilis%2C%20an%20executive%20at%20one%20of%20his%20startups%2C%20from%20Grimes%20and%20the%20singer%20only%20learned%20of%20it%20when%20it%20was%20revealed%20by%20Insider%20last%20year.%20Both%20Zilis%20and%20Grimes'%20surrogates%20were%20pregnant%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrimes%20also%20referenced%20Zilis%20in%20her%20post%20on%20X%2C%20saying%20she'd%20never%20even%20been%20%26quot%3Ballowed%26quot%3B%20to%20see%20pictures%20of%20Zilis'%20children%20with%20Musk%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20was%20%26quot%3Bripping%20my%20family%20apart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrimes%20and%20Zilis%20later%20appeared%20to%20address%20the%20situation%20on%20social%20media%2C%20saying%20on%20September%2010%20that%20they%20were%20no%20longer%20feuding.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMusk%20never%20responded%20to%20Grimes'%20comments%20on%20X.%20Just%20three%20days%20prior%2C%20he%20had%20filed%20his%20suit%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-asked-for-relationship-grimes-kids-in-secret-lawsuit-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696551468000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651f4fd66e038039826b0674%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-asked-for-relationship-grimes-kids-in-secret-lawsuit-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Grimes'%20custody%20lawsuit%20against%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20been%20widely%20reported%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20sued%20her%20first%2C%20Insider%20has%20learned%2C%20asking%20a%20Texas%20judge%20to%20set%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bparent-child%20relationship.%26qu