hase%20of%20Twitter%20and%20attempting%20to%20force%20him%20to%20sit%20for%20questioning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224623%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6507b0fdf05aa00019bddd62%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222919%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk.%3Cp%3EChesnot%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20SEC%20is%20investigating%20Elon%20Musk's%20initial%20investment%20in%20Twitter%20and%20his%20eventual%20takeover.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20government%20agency%20says%20Musk%20has%20failed%20to%20sit%20for%20an%20interview%20regarding%20the%20case.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk's%20lawyer%20Alex%20Spiro%20called%20the%20entire%20investigation%C2%A0%26quot%3Bmisguided.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E's%20investment%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-bizarre-change-x-twitter-ditch-article-headlines-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20eventual%20%2444%20billion%20acquisition%20of%20the%20platform%20is%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%2C%20with%20whom%20Musk%20now%20refuses%20to%20sit%20for%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsecurities-and-exchange-commission%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESEC%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20asked%20a%20California%20federal%20court%20to%20force%20Musk%2C%20who%20acquired%20Twitter%2C%20or%20X%2C%20just%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-chops-twitter-down-1000-employees-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20year%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20comply%20with%20a%20May%20subpoena%20asking%20him%20to%20sit%20for%20testimony.%20The%20filing%20revealed%20what%20the%20agency%20said%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Ban%20ongoing%20nonpublic%20investigation%20by%20the%20SEC%20regarding%20whether%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20Musk%20violated%20various%20provisions%20of%20the%20federal%20securities%20laws%26quot%3B%20with%20his%20initial%20secret%20collection%20of%20Twitter%20stock%20in%20early%202022%20and%20his%20later%20purchase%20of%20the%20company%2C%20along%20with%20statements%20he%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter-discussed-deal-50-a-share-talks-ended-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabout%20the%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20was%20noted%20last%20year%20in%20a%20filing%20in%20a%20separate%20court%20action%20that%20Musk%20was%20under%20federal%20investigation%2C%20it%20did%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2022%2Foct%2F13%2Felon-musk-investigation-twitter-takeover-deal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20disclose%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20which%20body%20or%20what%20the%20investigation%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SEC%20seeks%20Musk's%20testimony%20to%20obtain%20information%20not%20already%20in%20the%20SEC's%20possession%20that%20is%20relevant%20to%20its%20lawful%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20SEC%20has%20followed%20all%20appropriate%20administrative%20steps%20required%20in%20seeking%20Musk's%20testimony.%20In%20the%20face%20of%20Musk's%20blatant%20refusal%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20SEC's%20subpoena%2C%20the%20SEC%20now%20asks%20the%20Court%20to%20intervene%20and%20compel%20Musk's%20compliance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Musk%20previously%20gave%20the%20SEC%20a%20half-day%20of%20testimony%20in%20July%20of%202022%20related%20to%20its%20investigation%2C%20the%20agency%20said%20it%20is%20requesting%20he%20submit%20to%20further%20questioning%20because%20of%20the%20huge%20amount%20of%20additional%20information%20it's%20received%20this%20year.%20The%20SEC%20has%20%26quot%3Bthousands%20of%20new%20documents%20from%20various%20parties%20as%20part%20of%20its%20investigation%2C%20including%20hundreds%20of%20new%20documents%20produced%20by%20Musk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SEC%20has%20not%20yet%20had%20an%20opportunity%20to%20question%20Musk%20about%20those%20documents%20and%20other%20substantial%20information%20it%20has%20obtained%20in%20its%20investigation%20since%20July%2027%2C%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said%20in%20its%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20back%20and%20forth%20with%20Musk's%20lawyer%2C%20who%20the%20SEC%20claims%20never%20objected%20to%20Musk%20sitting%20for%20another%20interview%2C%20the%20Tesla%20billionaire%20agreed%20to%20be%20questioned%20on%20Sept.%2015%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20He%20did%20not%20appear%20for%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20lawyer%2C%20Alex%20Spiro%2C%20told%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20SEC%20has%20already%20taken%20Mr.%20Musk's%20testimony%20multiple%20times%20in%20this%20misguided%20investigation%20%E2%80%94%20enough%20is%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Spurious%20objections'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20two%20days%20before%20his%20scheduled%20testimony%2C%20Musk%20abruptly%20notified%20the%20SEC%20staff%20that%20he%20would%20not%20appear%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20SEC%20said.%20%26quot%3BMusk%20attempted%20to%20justify%20his%20refusal%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20subpoena%20by%20raising%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20several%20spurious%20objections%2C%20including%20an%20objection%20to%20San%20Francisco%20as%20an%20appropriate%20testimony%20location.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20of%20Musk's%20objections%20included%20that%20the%20SEC%20was%20attempting%20to%20%26quot%3Bharass%26quot%3B%20him%20and%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-buying-twitter-was-insane-he-lacks-empathy-biog