%20trial%20in%20a%20federal%20court%20in%20downtown%20Manhattan.%3Cp%3EChelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%20Research%20employee%20testified%20Thursday%20about%20a%20tense%20exchange%20with%20SBF.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20bulletproof%2C%26quot%3B%20Bankman-Fried%20said%20after%20discovering%20understated%20crypto%20losses%20at%20Alameda.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20incorrect%20balance%20sheet%20all%20started%20because%20of%20a%20programming%20bug%2C%20ex-employee%20Adam%20Yedidia%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20paddleball%20game%20at%20a%20Bahamas%20resort%2C%20where%20they%20shared%20a%20%2435%20million%20apartment%2C%20Adam%20Yedidia%20confronted%20his%20boss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20months%20earlier%2C%20Yedidia%20had%20found%20a%20bug%20in%20the%20code%20he%20had%20written%20for%20FTX%2C%20the%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20where%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20developer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20code%20was%20supposed%20to%20automate%20the%20process%20of%20deposits%2C%20allowing%20customers%20to%20put%20money%20into%20their%20FTX%20accounts%20faster%20and%20alleviating%20employee%20workloads.%20But%20it%20introduced%20a%20major%20problem%3A%20In%20the%20internal%20ledger%20on%20FTX's%20exchange%2C%20the%20numbers%20for%20Alameda%20Research%2C%20a%20cryptocurrency%20hedge%20fund%2C%20were%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlameda%20Research%2C%20it%20was%20discovered%2C%20had%20%24500%20million%20more%20in%20liabilities%20than%20previously%20realized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20the%20bug%20was%20fixed%2C%20in%20June%202022%2C%20six%20months%20after%20its%20discovery%2C%20that%20figure%20had%20grown%20to%20%248%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20numbers%20seemed%20large%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Yedidia%20testified%20Thursday%20in%20a%20federal%20court%20in%20downtown%20Manhattan.%20%26quot%3BIt%20concerned%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20hut%20bet