%2Fsurging-costs-make-car-ownership-difficult-for-average-singaporeans%2Famp_articleshow%2F104196226.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsurging-costs-make-car-ownership-difficult-for-average-singaporeans%2Famp_articleshow%2F104196226.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'The%20greatest%20advertising%20you%20can%20get'%3A%20Small-business%20founders%20explain%20how%20to%20build%20and%20grow%20your%20company%20with%20referrals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Michael%20Nova%2C%20left%2C%20wearing%20a%20black%20suit%20and%20black%20tie%20and%20a%20headshot%20of%20Kirby%20Wilkerson%2C%20right%2C%20wearing%20a%20white%20top%20and%20blazer%20in%20front%20of%20green%20plants.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651c2e9b42ecf94db4767f03%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20Nova%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Nova%20Custom%20Printing%2C%20and%20Kirby%20Wilkerson%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20The%20Impact%20Kind.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Frest%20%40FrestStudio%20and%20Kirby%20Wilkerson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EAsking%20clients%20for%20referrals%20is%20an%20easy%20way%20for%20small%20businesses%20to%20market%20themselves.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EClients%20referred%20by%20their%20friends%20or%20family%20are%20often%20a%20better%20fit%20for%20your%20products%20or%20services.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EConsider%20offering%20incentives%20such%20as%20discounts%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20referral.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarketing-for-small-business%5C%22%3EMarketing%20for%20Small%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20exploring%20the%20basics%20of%20marketing%20strategy%20for%20SBOs%20to%20earn%20new%20customers%20and%20grow%20their%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Michael%20Nova%20started%20his%20event-planning%20business%20in%20New%20York%20City%20in%201995%2C%20he%20had%20no%20advertising%20budget.%20He%20asked%20his%20friends%20to%20spread%20the%20word%2C%20and%20the%20company%20took%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20was%20word%20of%20mouth%2C%26quot%3B%20Nova%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20friends%2C%20and%20friends%20of%20friends%2C%20referring%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%2030%20years%20later%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnovacustomlabelprinting.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENova%20Custom%20Printing%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20custom%20branding%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20design%2C%20and%20works%20with%20many%20major%20brands%2C%20including%20BMW%2C%20L'Or%C3%A9al%2C%20and%20American%20Express.%20Nova%20attributes%20his%20company's%20growth%20and%20longevity%20to%20doing%20good%20work%2C%20networking%2C%20and%20building%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20greatest%20advertising%20you%20can%20get%20is%20when%20one%20person%20tells%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20Nova%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20like%20it.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferral%20marketing%2C%20where%20businesses%20ask%20their%20customers%20to%20recommend%20them%20to%20others%2C%20is%20a%20low-cost%20way%20for%20small%20companies%20to%20expand%20their%20client%20base%20and%20grow%20brand%20awareness.%20In%20a%202021%20Nielsen%20survey%20of%20consumers%2C%20more%20than%20eight%20in%2010%20respondents%20said%20they%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nielsen.com%2Finsights%2F2021%2Fbeyond-martech-building-trust-with-consumers-and-engaging-where-sentiment-is-high%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrusted%20recommendations%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20people%20they%20knew%20over%20other%20marketing%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20two%20small-business%20owners%20seek%20out%20referrals%20and%20have%20used%20them%20to%20generate%20leads%20and%20build%20their%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFocus%20on%20doing%20a%20good%20job%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKirby%20Wilkerson's%20sister%20was%20her%20first%20client%20when%20she%20launched%20her%20public-relations%20agency%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.impactkind.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Impact%20Kind%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%202020.%20Wilkerson%20helped%20her%20sister%20get%20national%20media%20coverage%20for%20her%20business%2C%20and%20afterward%2C%20friends%20reached%20out%20about%20Wilkerson%20helping%20them%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20it%20was%20seeing%20what%20we%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilkerson%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Michigan%20and%20works%20mostly%20with%20company%20executives%20and%20small%20businesses%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20referrals%20are%20what%20catapulted%20our%20business.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferrals%20helped%20her%20more%20than%20double%20her%20revenue%2C%20she%20said.%20The%20volume%20of%20new%20client%20requests%20led%20her%20to%20create%20a%20wait%20list.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20referrals%20depends%20on%20not%20only%20offering%20and%20delivering%20a%20quality%20product%20or%20service%20but%20also%20%26quot%3Bexceeding%20expectations%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilkerson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20are%20happy%2C%20they'll%20naturally%20refer%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Nova%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20focus%20as%20a%20business%20has%20always%20been%20on%20treating%20people%20as%20you%20would%20like%20to%20be%20treated%20yourself.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EConnect%20with%20your%20ideal%20clients%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReferrals%20can%20reduce%20the%20time%20you%20spend%20pitching%20your%20company%20to%20prospective%20clients%2C%20Wilkerson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClients%20who%20are%20referred%20by%20friends%20or%20family%20are%20often%20a%20much%20better%20fit%20for%20your%20business%20than%20customers%20who%20simply%20find%20you%20online%2C%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20easy%2C%20and%20it's%20meaningful%20because%20somebody%20liked%20your%20work%20enough%20to%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20this%20is%20worth%20the%20money%2C'%26quot%3B%20Wilkerson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EConsider%20offering%20incentives%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWilkerson%20offers%20a%20discount%20to%20any%20referral%20who%20becomes%20a%20client.%20And%20the%20client%20who%20referred%20them%20receives%20a%20small%20percentage%20back%20on%20their%20campaigns%20each%20month%20for%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20it's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20more%20important%20is%20that%20you%20stay%20on%20a%20client's%20mind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Wilkerson%20said%20she%20believed%20many%20clients%20would%20continue%20making%20referrals%20and%20staying%20connected%20without%20incentives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAsk%20for%20referrals%20naturally%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20a%20project%2C%20Nova%20follows%20up%20with%20the%20client%20to%20make%20sure%20they're%20satisfied%20and%20discuss%20how%20they%20may%20work%20together%20in%20the%20future%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20also%20asks%20them%20to%20recommend%20him%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilkerson%20sends%20referral%20emails%20before%20a%20project%20is%20completed%2C%20keeping%20the%20tone%20friendly%20and%20asking%20clients%20whether%20they%20know%20anyone%20looking%20for%20a%20similar%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20them%20for%20their%20business%20when%20you're%20asking%20for%20the%20referral%2C%20and%20then%20thank%20them%20again%20for%20giving%20the%20referral%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsking%20for%20a%20referral%20may%20feel%20awkward%20and%20uncomfortable%20at%20first%2C%20but%20if%20you've%20built%20trust%20with%20your%20customers%2C%20most%20are%20happy%20to%20do%20it%2C%20Nova%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20boils%20down%20to%20building%20long-term%20business%20relationships%2C%26quot%3B%20Nova%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20those%20connections%20had%20been%20the%20%26quot%3Blifeblood%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20strive%20to%20become%20an%20ally%20to%20our%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20ourselves%20invaluable%20resources%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-business-founders-explain-grow-your-company-referrals-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696534652000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651c2ecc617692f0d03dae7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-business-founders-explain-grow-your-company-referrals-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Growing%20your%20company%20through%20referrals%20is%20a%20simple%20and%20powerful%20way%20to%20expand%20your%20client%20base%2C%20generate%20leads%2C%20and%20build%20lasting%20relationships.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Erica%20Sweeney)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-business-founders-explain-grow-your-company-referrals-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CDS%20Anil%20Chauhan%20underlines%20policy%20of%20'strategic%20autonomy'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696534393000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104196250%2Cimgsize-1516207.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fchief-of-defence-staff-anil-chauhan-underlines-policy-of-strategic-autonomy%2Farticleshow%2F104196210.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20Chief%20o