_articleshow%2F104195956.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbrooklyn-subway-shooter-who-wounded-10-faces-sentencing-on-terrorism-charges%2Famp_articleshow%2F104195956.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20Assertiveness%20More%20Evident%20With%20Its%20Rise%3A%20Chief%20Of%20Defence%20Staff%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChina's%20assertiveness%20is%20more%20evident%20now%20with%20its%20rise%2C%20and%20India%20will%20have%20to%20take%20this%20aspect%20into%20account%20in%20its%20overall%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20calculus%26quot%3B%2C%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20General%20Anil%20Chauhan%20said%20on%20Thursday%20while%20delving%20into%20various%20national%20security%20challenges%20and%20profound%20geopolitical%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelivering%20the%20annual%20Gen%20KV%20Krishna%20Rao%20memorial%20lecture%2C%20he%20also%20referred%20to%20India's%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20dispute%26quot%3B%20along%20the%20northern%20borders%20with%20China%20and%20suggested%20that%20New%20Delhi%20will%20have%20to%20play%20its%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20autonomy%26quot%3B%20card%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20strategic%20autonomy%20may%20be%20relevant%20to%20exploit%20opportunities%20rather%20than%20to%20take%20care%20of%20your%20threats.%20That's%20where%20the%20future%20should%20lie.%20We%20should%20be%20thinking%20about%20opportunities%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20all%20that%20I%20said%20comes%20with%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20caveat%20because%20of%20the%20northern%20neighbour.%20In%20this%20strategic%20calculus%2C%20India%20will%20have%20to%20take%20into%20account%20the%20emergence%20of%20China%20as%20a%20major%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina's%20assertiveness%20is%20more%20evident%20with%20its%20rise.%20India%20has%20a%20major%20dispute%20on%20its%20northern%20borders%20with%20China%20and%20will%20have%20to%20play%20the%20strategic%20autonomy%20card...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20disruptions%20in%20the%20global%20geopolitical%20order%2C%20Gen%20Chauhan%20also%20underlined%20the%20need%20for%20India%20to%20continue%20maintaining%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20autonomy%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20approach%20and%20highlighted%20how%20New%20Delhi%20was%20moving%20forward%20from%20its%20approach%20of%20%26quot%3Bnon-alignment%26quot%3B%20to%20an%20era%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bvishwamitra%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20friend%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20cited%20India's%20nuclear%20tests%20in%201998%2C%20its%20%26quot%3Bneutral%20and%20a%20nuanced%26quot%3B%20stand%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20and%20the%20decision%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20procurement%20of%20S-400%20missile%20systems%20from%20Moscow%20notwithstanding%20threats%20of%20sanctions%20as%20examples%20of%20the%20country%20exercising%20its%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20autonomy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20India%20has%20transited%20ahead%20from%20non-alignment%20of%20yesteryears%20to%20self-alignment%20as%20you%20said%20to%20maybe%20multi-alignment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20also%20summarised%20India's%20journey%20of%20being%20non-aligned%20to%20that%20of%20exercising%20strategic%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%20to%20summarise%20the%20journey%20of%20India%20from%20non-alignment%20to%20exercising%20of%20strategic%20autonomy%2C%20it%20can%20be%20based%20on%20what%20I%20can%20say%20is%20three%20S.%20First%20is%20securing%20India.%20Next%20is%20self-reliance.%20And%20lastly%2C%20shaping%20the%20environment%20to%20India's%20advantage%20and%20benefit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGen%20Chauhan%20also%20elaborated%20on%20economic%20aspects%20of%20global%20geopolitics%20and%20that%20the%20global%20balance%20of%20power%20can%20be%20shifted%20by%20economic%20alignment%20and%20even%20issues%20like%20morality%2C%20righteousness%20and%20convergence%20of%20global%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20India's%20famous%20epic%20Mahabharata%2C%20Lord%20Krishna%20shifted%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20towards%20the%20Pandavas.%20His%20military%20might%20went%20to%20the%20Kauravas%20but%20it%20was%20only%20his%20righteousness%20and%20sage%20advice%20which%20shifted%20the%20balance%20of%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20ultimately%20the%20Pandavas%20emerged%20victorious%20in%20that%20particular%20war.%20We%20as%20a%20nation%20have%20utilised%20the%20G20%20platform%20to%20leverage%20soft%20power%20to%20play%20a%20dominating%20role.%20So%20these%20are%20also%20important%20facts%20we%20must%20keep%20in%20mind%20when%20we%20take%20strategic%20decisions%20on%20how%20to%20get%20aligned%20in%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGen%20Chauhan%20said%20the%20global%20geopolitical%20environment%20is%20currently%20in%20a%20state%20of%20flux%20and%20India%20must%20exercise%20its%20options%20looking%20at%20its%20national%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20I%20believe%20is%20transiting%20between%20two%20orders.%20The%20old%20order%20is%20withering%20away%20and%20the%20shapes%20and%20no%20one%20knows%20the%20contours%20of%20this%20new%20order%20and%20how%20it%20will%20shape%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGen%20Chauhan%20also%20cited%20the%20financial%20crisis%2C%20disruptions%20in%20the%20global%20supply%20chains%20due%20to%20COVID-19%2C%20food%20and%20fertilizer%20shortages%20due%20to%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20as%20some%20of%20the%20manifestations%20of%20the%20geopolitical%20and%20geoeconomic%20flux.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E