%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fman-jailed-for-9-years-for-threatening-to-kill-queen-elizabeth-as-revenge-for-jallianwala-bagh%2Farticleshow%2F104194502.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SAT%20Quashes%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20Insider%20Trading%20Order%20Against%20NDTV%20Co-Founders%20Prannoy%20Roy%20and%20Radhika%20Roy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F02162103%2FUntitled-design-58-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Securities%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20(SAT)%20has%20quashed%20an%20insider%20trading%20order%20by%20capital%20markets%20regulator%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20against%20Prannoy%20Roy%20and%20Radhika%20Roy%2C%20the%20co-founders%20of%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20order%2C%20issued%20by%20SEBI%20in%20November%202020%2C%20accused%20them%20of%20insider%20trading%20and%20barred%20them%20from%20accessing%20the%20capital%20markets%20for%20two%20years.%20It%20had%20directed%20them%20to%20disgorge%20the%20amount%20wrongfully%20gained%20%E2%80%93%20over%20Rs%2016.97%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%206%25%20interest%20per%20annum.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsat-overturns-sebi-order-against-ndtv-founders-prannoy-roy-radhika-roy-123100500836_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20SAT%20overturned%20the%20order%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20information%20scrutinised%20by%20SEBI%20was%20not%20price-sensitive%2C%20and%20the%20Roys%20were%20not%20insiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20find%20that%20Prannoy%20Roy%20and%20Radhika%20Roy%20received%20pre-trade%20clearance%20from%20NDTV%E2%80%99s%20compliance%20officer%2C%20a%20fact%20acknowledged%20in%20the%20show%20cause%20notice.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20trad