%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-ndtv-prannoy-roy-radhika-roy-27cr-penalty-sebi-171783%5C%22%3Estayed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20recovery%20of%20penalty%20on%20the%20NDTV%20promoters.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696524569000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F02162103%2FUntitled-design-58-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsat-quashes-sebis-insider-trading-order-against-ndtv-co-founders-prannoy-roy-and-radhika-roy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SAT%20said%20that%20the%20information%20scrutinised%20by%20SEBI%20was%20not%20price-sensitive%2C%20and%20the%20Roys%20were%20not%20insiders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsat-quashes-sebis-insider-trading-order-against-ndtv-co-founders-prannoy-roy-and-radhika-roy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tiger-Kriti%20get%20groovy%20in%20Ganapath%20song%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696523330000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104194299%2Cimgsize-22558.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fganapath-tiger-shroff-and-kriti-sanon-are-here-to-slay-as-they-unveil-dance-number-hum-aaye-hain-watch%2Farticleshow%2F104194289.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104194289.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20makers%20of%20the%20film%20'Ganapath%3A%20A%20Hero%20is%20Born'%20have%20released%20the%20first%20track%20of%20the%20movie%20called%20'Hum%20Aaye%20Hain'.%20Actor%20Tiger%20Shroff%20shared%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20song%20on%20Instagram%2C%20featuring%20him%20and%20actress%20Kriti%20Sanon%20dancing%20in%20black%20outfits.%20The%20film%2C%20directed%20by%20Vikas%20Bahl%2C%20is%2