n%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20money%20in%20exchange%2C%20which%20was%20from%20the%20proceeds%20of%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahadev%20Online%20Book%20App%2C%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20controversy%2C%20is%20an%20umbrella%20syndicate%20arranging%20online%20platforms%20to%20enable%20illegal%20betting%20websites%20to%20enroll%20new%20users%2C%20create%20user%20IDs%2C%20and%20launder%20money%20through%20a%20layered%20web%20of%20benami%20bank%20accounts%2C%20the%20probe%20agency%20has%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPROMOTERS%20OF%20GAMING%20APP%20MADE%20RS%20200%20CRORE%20A%20DAY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20black%20money%20masterminds%20Sourabh%20Chandrakar%20and%20Ravi%20Uppal%20are%20two%20big%20names%20in%20the%20shady%20world%20of%20online%20betting%2C%20with%20their%20network%20not%20only%20in%20India%2C%20but%20also%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Nepal%2C%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20accused%20are%20residents%20of%20Chhattisgarh's%20Bhilai%20and%20surprisingly%2C%20till%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20Chandrakar%20ran%20a%20juice%20shop%2C%20while%20Uppal%20had%20a%20tyre%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20their%20savings%2C%20the%20two%20went%20to%20Dubai%20and%20met%20a%20sheikh%20and%20a%20Pakistani%20national%2C%20who%20eventually%20worked%20together%20to%20open%20the%20online%20betting%20app.%20Soon%2C%20Chandrakar%20and%20Uppal%20made%20a%20%26quot%3Bname%26quot%3B%20for%20themselves%20in%20the%20betting%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ED%2C%20the%20two%20set%20up%20a%20network%20of%20around%204%2C000%20panel%20operators%20in%20India%20for%20online%20betting.%20Each%20operator%20had%20200%20customers%20who%20placed%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpromoters-of-apps-that-made-rs-200-crore-a-day-once-ran-juice-tyre-shops-4453322%5C%22%3ESoon%2C%20the%20two%20were%20making%20at%20least%20Rs%20200%20crore%20a%20day.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chandrakar%20got%20married%20in%20the%20UAE%20this%20February%2C%20he%20allegedly%20spent%20Rs%20200%20crore%20in%20cash%20on%20the%20grand%20wedding.%20Private%20jets%20flew%20guests%20from%20India%20to%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20wedding%20planners%2C%20dancers%2C%20decorators%2C%20and%20others%20were%20paid%20through%20Hawala%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFourteen%20Bollywood%20celebrities%20were%20invited%20to%20perform%20at%20the%20wedding.%20All%20are%20under%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20radar%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20investigators%20seized%20assets%20worth%20Rs%20417%20crore%20in%20raids%20at%2039%20locations%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20and%20Bhopal%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Mahadev%20online%20betting%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696522740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F4s604dho_kapil-sharma-huma-qureshi-hina-khan_625x300_05_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkapil-sharma-huma-qureshi-hina-khan-summoned-in-mahadev-app-case-sources-4453662%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Comedian-actor%20Kapil%20Sharma%20and%20actors%20Huma%20Qureshi%20and%20Hina%20Khan%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20or%20ED%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20case%20involving%20the%20Mahadev%20gaming%20app%2C%20sources%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkapil-sharma-huma-qureshi-hina-khan-summoned-in-mahadev-app-case-sources-4453662%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkapil-sharma-huma-qureshi-hina-khan-summoned-in-mahadev-app-case-sources-4453662%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkapil-sharma-huma-qureshi-hina-khan-summoned-in-mahadev-app-case-sources-4453662%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Decade%20Before%20Sikkim%20Flash%20Floods%2C%20There%20Were%20Warnings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsikkim-flash-floods%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESikkim%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20burst%20its%20boundaries%20early%20Wednesday%20-%20killing%2014%20people%20and%20destroying%20a%20hydroelectric%20project%20worth%20thousands%20of%20crores%20-%20displayed%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20high%20probability%20of%20sudden%20outburst%26quot%3B%20that%20could%20trigger%20flash%20floods%20downstream%2C%20scientists%20warned%20back%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20there%20were%20warnings%20even%20as%20far%20back%20as%202001%3B%20the%20Sikkim%20Human%20Development%20Report%20spoke%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bcatastrophic%26quot%3B%20impact%20of%20glacial%20lake%20outburst%20floods%2C%20or%20GLOF%2C%20and%20highlighted%20the%20state's%20Onglokthang%2C%20Rathong%20Chu%20and%20Zemu%20glaciers%2C%20which%20had%20even%20then%20retreated%20by%20several%20kilometres.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20GLOF%20occurs%20when%20lakes%20formed%20by%20melting%20glaciers%20suddenly%20burst%20open%20due%20to%20various%20reasons%2C%20including%20excessive%20water%20accumulation%20(from%20cloudbursts)%20or%20triggers%20like%20earthquakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20bursts%2C%20it%20releases%20an%20enormous%20volume%20of%20water%20all%20at%20once%2C%20causing%20flash%20floods%20downstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBack%20to%20the%20(relative)%20present%2C%20the%20Sikkim%20government's%20Department%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%20issued%20a%20warning%20in%202016%20and%2C%20in%202021%2C%20a%20study%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0169555X21001914%3Fref%3Dpdf_download%26fr%3DRR-2%26rr%3D8116a426a8038e90%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeomorphology%3C%2Fa%3E%20red-flagged%20%26quot%3Baccelerated%20growth%26quot%3B%20of%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20the%20state%20and%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20glacier.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3ERetreating%20Lhonak%20Glaciers%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20Lhonak%20glacier%20receded%201.9%20-%202%20km%20between%201962%20and%202008%20and%20400m%20more%20in%20the%20following%2011%20years%2C%20the%20scientists%20behind%20the%202013%20and%202021%20studies%20said.%20What%20this%20basically%20means%20is%20the%20glacier%20melted%20-%20due%20to%20climate%20change%20and%20global%20warming%20-%20and%20increased%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20in%20the%20lake.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsikkim-flash-floods-lhonak-lake-isros-satellite-images-show-how-sikkims-lhonak-lake-burst-caused-floods-4450175%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EISRO's%20Satellite%20Images%20Show%20How%20Sikkim's%20Lhonak%20Lake%20Burst%2C%20Caused%20Floods%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESituated%2017%2C100%20feet%20above%20sea%20level%2C%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20was%20also%20fed%20by%20glacial%20run-off%20from%20the%20retreating%20North%20Lhonak%20glacier%20and%20the%20main%20Lhonak%20glacier.%20This%20increased%20the%20lake's%20surface%20area%20by%20500%20metres%20and%20average%20depth%20by%2050%20metres%2C%20Dr%20SN%20Remya%2C%20the%20lead%20scientist%20of%20the%202013%20paper%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fradcc55g_sikkim-flood-graphic_625x300_05_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20predicted%20(in%202013)%20the%20probability%20of%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20glacier%20breaking%20is%2042%20per%20cent.%20Regarding%20the%20lake%20burst%20in%20Sikkim%2C%20we%20predicted%20it%20would%20result%20in%20the%20release%20of%20up%20to%2019%20million%20cubic%20meters%20of%20water.%20We%20had%20said%20this%20lake%20is%20in%20danger...%20recommended%20early%20warning%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EHow%20Much%20Water%20In%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ESatellite%20images%20released%20Wednesday%20by%20space%20agency%20ISRO%20showed%20the%20lake%20held%20nearly%20170%20hectares%20of%20water%20less%20than%20a%20week%20before%20a%20cloudburst%20broke%2C%20so%20to%20speak%2C%20tipped%20the%20scales.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20morning%20-%20hours%20after%20the%20lake%20burst%20-%20there%20are%20only%2060.3%20hectares%20of%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fimkj1qp_sikkim-lhonak-lake-isro-satellite-photo_625x300_04_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Remya's%20study%20had%20predicted%20a%20peak%20discharge%20of%20nearly%20600%20cubic%20metres%20of%20water%20per%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%202021%20study%20predicted%20a%20peak%20discharge%20seven%20times%20worse%20-%20around%204%2C300%20cubic%20metres%20per%20second%20for%20a%20breach%20depth%20of%2020%20metres%20-%20and%20a%20terrifying%2012%2C500%20cubic%20metres%20for%2050%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Sikkim%2C%20lake-terminating%20glaciers%20have%20shown%20accelerated%20growth...%20South%20Lhonak%20glacier%20is%20no%20different.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-retreating%20glaciers%20and%20the%20associated%20proglacial%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20has%20become%20the%20largest%20and%20fastest-growing%20in%20the%20state...%20this%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20hazard%20potentials%20as%20downstream%20(areas)%20are%20heavily%20populated...%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20highlighted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EFlash%20Floods%20Wreak%20Havoc%20In%20Sikkim%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20resulting%20flash%20flood%20not%20only%20washed%20the%20Chungthang%20power%20station%2C%20killed%2014%20people%20and%20left%20(as%20of%20late%20Thursday%20night)%20over%20a%20100%20missing%2C%20and%20destroyed%20key%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20remote%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsikkim-flood-sikkim-flash-flood-teesta-river-dam-parts-of-teesta-river-dam-washed-away-after-cloudburst-in-sikkim-4448215%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParts%20Of%20Teesta%20River%20Dam%20Washed%20Away%20After%20Cloudburst%20In%20Sikkim%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReports%20indicate%20the%20Sikkim%20government%20did%20take%20some%20preventive%20measures%2C%20including%20siphoning%20some%20of%20the%20excess%20water%20from%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20after%20an%20expedition%20in%202016.%20And%2C%20just%20last%20month%2C%20government%20officials%20and%20scientists%20planned%20to%20install%20early%20warning%20systems%20at%20the%20lake.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsikkim-flood-sikkim-floods-cloudburst-lake-burst-and-a-damaged-dam-how-sikkim-flash-flood-happened-4453285%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20Sikkim%20Flash%20Flood%20Happened%3A%20Explained%20In%20Graphics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20they%20could%2C%20though%2C%20came%20that%20fateful%20cloudburst%20-%20part%20of%20unseasonal%20rainfall%20that%20saw%20northern%20Sikkim%20(where%20the%20lake%20is)%20get%2050%20per%20cent%20more%20rain%20than%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fbbdn63i_sikkim-flood-graphic_625x300_05_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESikkim%20has%20300%20g