%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20Congress%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20final%20voter%20list%2C%20alleging%20multiple%20entries%20of%20voters.%20The%20Congress%20alleged%20that%20the%20actual%20number%20of%20voters%20in%20the%20state%20is%20much%20lesser%20than%203%2C17%2C17%2C389%20published%20by%20the%20EC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20issue%20of%20voter%20list%20discrepancies%20is%20not%20new%2C%20as%20the%202018%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Telangana%20also%20saw%2022%20lakh%20voter%20names%20deleted%20without%20informing%20the%20voters.%20The%20then%20CEO%2C%20Rajat%20Kumar%2C%20had%20acknowledged%20that%20many%20voters%20could%20indeed%20not%20exercise%20their%20right%20and%20issued%20an%20apology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20senior%20vice%20president%20G.%20Niranjan%20told%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20party%20would%20conduct%20a%20survey%20of%20its%20own%20and%20approach%20the%20Telangana%20high%20court%20to%20refute%20the%20EC%E2%80%99s%20voter%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20we%20brought%20up%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20GHMC%20Commissioner%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20District%20Election%20officer%20for%20the%20Hyderabad%20District%2C%20we%20were%20informed%20that%203%2C175%20multiple%20entries%20were%20found%20on%20verification%20in%20the%20Bahadurpura%20constituency%20alone%2C%20of%20which%20roughly%202%2C120%20are%20still%20not%20cleared%2C%E2%80%9D%20Niranjan%20told%20%3Cem%3ETNM.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20written%20to%20Telangana%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20Feroz%20Khan%2C%20the%20CEO%20mentioned%20that%20in%20the%20Nampally%20constituency%20under%20Hyderabad%20district%2C%20there%20are%2046%2C%20396%20additional%20names%20in%20the%20electoral%20list%20as%20of%20September%201%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696521543000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2