px-Supreme_Court_of_India_01.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20October%205%20(Thursday)%20asked%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20%E2%80%9Chow%20will%20they%20establish%20money%20laundering%20by%20%5BAam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%5D%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20factually%20and%20legally%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESisodia%20is%20in%20judicial%20custody%20over%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20excise%20policy%20scam%20case.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcbi-arrests-manish-sisodia-delhi-deputy-cm%5C%22%3Ewas%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20February%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20asked%20the%20central%20probe%20agencies%20whether%20there%20was%20any%20evidence%20to%20connect%20the%20proceeds%20of%20the%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20activity%20with%20the%20AAP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20will%20you%20establish%20money%20laundering%20by%20Sisodia%20factually%20and%20legally%3F%E2%80%A6%20He%20may%20be%20aware%20it%20may%20be%20used%2C%20as%20per%20your%20case%2C%20but%20he%20never%20came%20in%20actual%20physical%20possession%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20SVN%20Bhatti%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fmanish-sisodia-bail-plea-supreme-court-says-no-offence-would-lie-without-evidence-bribery%5C%22%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20made%20these%20remarks%20while%20hearing%20bail%20pleas%20filed%20by%20AAP%20leader%20and%20former%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20policy%20decision%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-manish-sisodia-money-laundering-pmla-delhi-liquor-policy-scm-239427%5C%22%3E%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20top%20court%20sought%20clarification%20regarding%20the%20nature%20of%20submissions%20of%20the%20investigative%20agencies.%20Justice%20Khanna%20asked%20if%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20Excise%20Policy%20for%202021-22%20was%20under%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20(ASG)%20S.V.%20Raju%2C%20who%20appeared%20for%20the%20two%20agencies%2C%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20agencies%20were%20not%20challenging%20the%20policy%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20then%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20you%20say%20that%20policy%20decision%20was%20motivated%20for%20personal%20benefits.%20So%20will%20it%20not%20mean%20that%20you%E2%80%99re%20challenging%20the%20policy%20decision%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ASG%20said%20that%20the%20submission%20forwarded%20by%20the%20agencies%20was%20that%20the%20policy%20in%20question%20was%20framed%20in%20a%20manner%20which%20benefitted%20certain%20wholesalers%20and%20Sisodia%20had%20a%20role%20to%20play%20in%20the%20same.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20policy%20was%20framed%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfacade%E2%80%9D%20to%20replace%20the%20old%20excise%20policy%20which%20was%20not%20favoured%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20old%20policy%20was%20not%20what%20they%20wanted.%20To%20change%20the%20policy%20they%20got%20Dhawan%20committee%20report%20but%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20what%20they%20wanted.%20So%20then%20they%20invited%20objections%20and%20suggestions.%20In%20those%20objections%20we%20see%20the%20role%20of%20the%20petitioner%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20ASG%2C%20per%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20understand%20that%20there%20is%20a%20policy%20change.%20Everyone%20will%20support%20policies%20good%20for%20their%20business.%20Pressure%20groups%20are%20always%20there.%20Policy%20changes%20even%20if%20wrong%2C%20without%20money%20consideration%20will%20not%20matter.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20money%20part%20which%20makes%20it%20an%20offence.%20If%20we%20go%20to%20an%20extent%20to%20say%20that%20there%20cannot%20be%20any%20pressure%20groups%2C%20no%20government%20can%20continue%E2%80%A6Lobbying%20will%20always%20be%20there.%20Of%20course%20we%E2%80%99re%20not%20saying%20that%20bribes%20can%20be%20accepted%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%20Vijay%20Nair%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98s%20role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ASG%20submitted%20that%20as%20per%20an%20approver%E2%80%99s%20statement%2C%20Vijay%20Nair%20was%20working%20on%20behalf%20of%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhose%20statement%20is%20that%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20his%20opinion.%20Two%20questions%20in%20the%20cross%20examination%20and%20this%20will%20fall%20flat.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20opinion%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20an%20expert.%20Expert%20opinion%20is%20different.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20inference%20drawn.%20His%20opinion%20does%20not%20matter.%20The%20court%E2%80%99s%20opinion%20matters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EASG%20Raju%20argued%20that%20Nair%20was%20given%20a%20bungalow%20next%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20bungalow%20and%20he%20operated%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20somebody%20who%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%20So%20if%20somebody%20says%20he%20is%20connected%20to%20Deputy%20CM%E2%80%A6see%20how%20he%20is%20operating.%20They%20are%20having%20the%20GoM%20policy%20even%20before%20the%20policy%20was%20released.%20This%20shows%20that%20they%20had%20a%20role%20to%20play%20in%20the%20policy%2C%E2%80%9D%20ASG%20Raju%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20you%20bring%20Sisodia%20under%20PMLA%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CManish%20Sisodia%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20all%20this.%20Vijay%20Nair%20is%20there%20but%20Manish%20Sisodia%20is%20not%20in%20this%20part.%20How%20will%20you%20bring%20him%20under%20money%20laundering%20Act%3F%20The%20money%20is%20not%20going%20to%20him.%20In%20case%20it%20is%20a%20company%20with%20whom%20he%20is%20involved%2C%20then%20we%20have%20vicarious%20liability.%20Otherwise%20the%20prosecution%20falters.%20Money%20laundering%20is%20entirely%20a%20different%20offence%E2%80%A6We%20have%20to%20show%20that%20he%20is%20in%20possession%20of%20that%20property.%20You%20will%20have%20to%20go%20to%20the%20exact%20wording%20of%20the%20section%20and%20show%20how%20will%20you%20bring%20him%20in.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20added%20that%20PMLA%20dealt%20with%20process%20or%20activity%20connected%20with%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20and%20not%20%E2%80%9Cgeneration%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20not%20got%20the%20possession%2C%20somebody%20else%20has.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20acquisition%20by%20him%2C%20it%20is%20acquisition%20by%20someone%20else.%20Use%20is%20by%20someone%20else.%20Projecting%20is%20by%20someone%20else%E2%80%A6Generation%20is%20not%20a%20part%20of%20it.%20Concealment%20is%20a%20part%20of%20it.%20Possibly%20you%20can%20bring%20it%20under%20concealement%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20said-%20Abetment%20is%20separate%2C%20vicarious%20liability%20is%20separate%2C%20principal%20offender%20may%20be%20someone%20separate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ASG%20said%20that%C2%A0%E2%80%9Che%20is%20involved%20in%20a%20process%20or%20activity%20which%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGeneration%20of%20money%20is%20not%20an%20offence%20under%20Section%203%20(of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2F%20PMLA)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20apex%20court%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20give%20bribe%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20involved%20in%20the%20activity%20connected%20to%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%20Suppose%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20assume%2C%20ultimately%20no%20money%20is%20passed%20on.%20Will%20PMLA%20trigger%3F%20What%20triggers%20in%20PMLA%20is%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20PMLA%20will%20be%20triggered%20after%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20are%20given%20or%20paid.%20You%20have%20to%20connect%20the%20person%20concerned%20with%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crimes%2C%20directly%20or%20indirectly.%20Abetment%2C%20it%20may%20be.%20But%20as%20a%20principal%20offender%20it%20will%20be%20a%20different%20situation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20will%20be%20next%20heard%20on%20October%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696519212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02102630%2F1156px-Supreme_Court_of_India_01.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fno-money-has-come-to-manish-sisodia-how-will-you-bring-him-under-pmla-sc-to-ed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20is%20in%20judicial%20custody%20over%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20excise%20policy%20scam%20case.%20He%20was%20arrested%20on%20February%2026.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fno-money-has-come-to-manish-sisodia-how-will-you-bring-him-under-pmla-sc-to-ed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20MLA's%20Aide%20Dug%20Up%20Road%20In%20UP%20Because%20He%20Didn't%20Get%20%26quot%3BCommission%26quot%3B%3A%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20half-a-kilometre%20stretch%20of%20a%20road%20being%20laid%20by%20the%20public%20works%20department%20(PWD)%2C%20connecting%20Shahjahanpur%20to%20Budaun%2C%20was%20dug%20up%20with%20the%20help%20of%20bulldozers%20allegedly%20by%20a%20representative%20of%20a%20BJP%20MLA%20for%20non-payment%20of%20%26quot%3Bcommission%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20contractor%20in%20this%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20on%20a%20complaint%20from%20Ramesh%20Singh%2C%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20construction%20company%2C%20against%2015-20%20unidentified%20people.%20The%20complainant%20has%20alleged%20that%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20is%20the%20representative%20of%20Veer%20Vikram%20Singh%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MLA%20from%20Katra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20under%20the%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20and%20Prevention%20of%20Damage%20to%20Public%20Property%20Act%20on%20October%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20has%20alleged%20that%20Jagveer%20Singh%2C%20who%20introduced%20himself%20as%20the%20representative%20of%20the%20MLA%2C%20intimidated%20the%20employees%20of%20the%20construction%20company%20on%20several%20occasions%20and%20demanded%20a%20%26quot%3B5%20per%20cent%20commission%26quot%3B%20(money%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20construction%20work)%20from%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20this%20commission%20was%20not%20given%2C%20they%20dug%20up%20half%20a%20kilometre%20of%20the%20road%20built%20by%20us%20with%20bulldozers%20on%20October%202%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged%20in%20his%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EQuoting%20from%20the%20FIR%2C%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SP)%20Ashok%20Kumar%20Meena%20told%20PTI%20that%20the%20road%20is%20being%20constructed%20from%20Jaitipur%20via%20Nawada%20to%20Budaun%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20alleged%20that%20Jagveer%20Singh%20reached%20the%20road%20construction%20site%20with%2015%20to%2020%20men%2C%20beat%20up%20the%20workers%20engaged%20in%20the%20work%20with%20sticks%20and%20dug%20half%20a%20kilometre%20of%20the%20road%20with%20bulldozers%2C%20the%20SP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20attempts%20are%20on%20to%20arrest%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20District%20Magistrate%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Pandey%20said%20detailed%20information%20has%20been%20so