ig%20names%20in%20the%20shady%20world%20of%20online%20betting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20network%20is%20not%20only%20in%20India%20but%20also%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Nepal%20and%20Pakistan.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20is%20looking%20for%20the%20two%20men%20and%20has%20issued%20non-bailable%20warrants%20and%20lookout%20circulars.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20accused%20are%20residents%20of%20Chhattisgarh's%20Bhilai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20till%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20Sourabh%20Chandrakar%20had%20been%20running%20a%20juice%20shop%20in%20Bhilai's%20Nehru%20Nagar%2C%20while%20Ravi%20Uppal%20owned%20a%20tyre%20shop.%20Investigators%20said%20both%20became%20addicted%20to%20gambling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20whatever%20savings%20they%20had%2C%20the%20two%20men%20went%20to%20Dubai%20and%20met%20a%20sheikh%20and%20a%20Pakistani%20national%2C%20who%20eventually%20worked%20together%20to%20open%20the%20Mahadev%20online%20betting%20app.%20Soon%2C%20Sourabh%20Chandrakar%20and%20Ravi%20Uppal%20made%20a%20'name'%20for%20themselves%20in%20the%20betting%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20said%20the%20two%20men%20set%20up%20a%20network%20of%20some%204%2C000%20panel%20operators%20in%20India%20for%20online%20betting.%20Each%20panel%20operator%20has%20200%20customers%20who%20place%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUsing%20this%20method%2C%20the%20two%20had%20been%20making%20at%20least%20Rs%20200%20crore%20daily%20and%20managed%20to%20build%20an%20'empire'%20in%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sourabh%20Chandrakar%20got%20married%20in%20February%20this%20year%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20he%20allegedly%20spent%20Rs%20200%20crore%20in%20cash%20to%20organise%20a%20grand%20wedding%20ceremony.%20He%20hired%20a%20private%20jet%20to%20fly%20his%20family%20from%20Bhilai%20and%20Nagpur%20to%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHawala%20channels%20were%20used%20to%20pay%20wedding%20planners%2C%20dancers%2C%20decorators%2C%20etc.%20A%20hawala%20transaction%20refers%20to%20a%20financial%20crime%20when%20money%20changes%20hands%20without%20entering%20the%20formal%20banking%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESourabh%20Chandrakar%20invited%2014%20Bollywood%20celebrities%20to%20perform%20at%20the%20wedding%3B%20all%20are%20under%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20radar%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20investigators%20seized%20assets%20worth%20Rs%20417%20crore%20by%20raiding%2039%20locations%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Kolkata%20and%20Bhopal%20in%20the%20Mahadev%20online%20betting%20app%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20Chandrakar%20and%20Ravi%20Uppal%20are%20hiding%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20investigation%20has%20shown%20that%20Mahadev%20Online%20Book%20App%20is%20run%20from%20a%20central%20head%20office%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20officials%20said.%20It%20operates%20by%20franchising%20%26quot%3BPanel%2FBranches%26quot%3B%20to%20their%20known%20associates%20on%2070-30%20per%20cent%20profit%20ratio%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696512720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fpjth75rg_mahadev-app_625x300_15_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpromoters-of-apps-that-made-rs-200-crore-a-day-once-ran-juice-tyre-shops-4453322%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20summons%20to%20actor%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20in%20the%20Mahadev%20online%20betting%20app%20case%20has%20created%20a%20buzz%20over%20this%20company%20that%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20money%20laundering.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpromoters-of-apps-that-made-rs-200-crore-a-day-once-ran-juice-tyre-shops-4453322%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpromoters-of-apps-that-made-rs-200-crore-a-day-once-ran-juice-tyre-shops-4453322%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpromoters-of-apps-that-made-rs-200-crore-a-day-once-ran-juice-tyre-shops-4453322%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Study%20Claims%20University%20Graduates%20In%20US%20Live%20Longer%20Than%20Non-Graduates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20study%20conducted%20by%20two%20economists%20at%20Princeton%20University%20has%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20disparity%20in%20life%20expectancy%20between%20people%20with%20college%20degrees%20and%20those%20without%20it%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fgraphic-detail%2F2023%2F10%2F02%2Famericas-university-graduates-live-much-longer-than-non-graduates%5C%22%3EThe%20Economist%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Esaid%20in%20a%20report.%20The%20study%20is%20based%20on%20an%20analysis%20of%20demographic%20data%20in%20the%20US.%20It%20said%20that%20despite%20robust%20economic%20performance%20in%20the%20United%20States%20in%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20particularly%20its%20economic%20growth%2C%20measures%20of%20wellness%2C%20notably%20life%20expectancy%2C%20have%20appeared%20less%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20by%20Princeton%20economists%20Anne%20Case%20and%20Angus%20Deaton%20said%20that%20in%202021%2C%2025-year-old%20Americans%20without%20a%20four-year%20college%20degree%20were%20expected%20to%20live%20approximately%2010%20years%20less%20on%20average%20than%20their%20college-educated%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20research%20builds%20upon%20a%20trend%20that%20has%20become%20increasingly%20apparent%20as%20Covid-19%20has%20impacted%20life%20expectancy%2C%20which%20is%20derived%20from%20mortality%20data%20at%20various%20ages.%20Despite%20the%20nation's%20growing%20wealth%2C%20the%20United%20States%20has%20been%20falling%20behind%20other%20industrialised%20countries%20in%20terms%20of%20life%20expectancy.%20A%20generation%20ago%2C%20the%20US%20ranked%20in%20the%20middle%20among%20these%20nations%2C%20but%20it%20now%20lags%20behind%20most%20other%20wealthy%20countries%2C%20said%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Economist%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Even%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20Americans'%20likelihood%20of%20premature%20death%20was%20increasing%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20gradual%20decline%20in%20life%20expectancy.%20Higher%20mortality%20rates%20were%20attributed%20to%20factors%20such%20as%20drug%20overdoses%2C%20shootings%2C%20and%20car%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20study's%20authors%20note%20that%20%26quot%3BAmericans%20with%20a%20college%20degree%2C%20if%20they%20were%20a%20separate%20country%2C%20would%20be%20one%20of%20the%20best%20performers%2C%20just%20below%20Japan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20largely%20attributed%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20graduates%20tend%20to%20have%20higher%20incomes%20and%20are%20better%20equipped%20to%20protect%20themselves%20from%20various%20dangers%20compared%20to%20non-graduates.%20However%2C%20the%20outlet%20noted%20that%20Americans%20with%20degrees%20still%20face%20a%20higher%20likelihood%20of%20falling%20victim%20to%20violence%20or%20drug%20overdoses%20compared%20to%20their%20counterparts%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20if%20not%20necessarily%20succumbing%20to%20cancer.%20This%20underscores%20the%20role%20of%20inequality%20as%20a%20key%20factor%20contributing%20to%20the%20overall%20decline%20in%20American%20mortality%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Economist%3C%2Fem%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696512720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F589ll6e_graduation-_625x300_28_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fstudy-claims-university-graduates-in-us-live-longer-than-non-graduates-4453362%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Higher%20mortality%20rates%20were%20attributed%20to%20factors%20such%20as%20drug%20overdoses%2C%20shootings%2C%20and%20car%20accidents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fs