ant%20Singh%20Chail%2C%20who%20attempted%20to%20assassinate%20the%20late%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II%20with%20a%20crossbow%20on%20Christmas%20Day%20in%202021%2C%20has%20been%20sentenced%20for%20treason%20at%20the%20Old%20Bailey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhat-was-the-amritsar-massacre-the-event-that-led-a-man-to-try-to-kill-the-queen-12960593%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhat-was-the-amritsar-massacre-the-event-that-led-a-man-to-try-to-kill-the-queen-12960593%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhat-was-the-amritsar-massacre-the-event-that-led-a-man-to-try-to-kill-the-queen-12960593%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt%20Is%20Not%20Like%20We%20Are%20In%20India...%26quot%3B%3A%20Babar%20Bowled%20Over%20By%20Fans'%20Welcome%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOverwhelmed%20with%20hospitality%20since%20arriving%20in%20India%2C%20Babar%20Azam%20is%20completely%20feeling%20%26quot%3Bat%20home%26quot%3B%20in%20Hyderabad%20but%20didn't%20forgot%20to%20add%20that%20Pakistan%20cricket%20fans%20have%20been%20missed%20amid%20their%20build-up%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%20The%20Babar-led%20Pakistan%20side%20has%20been%20based%20in%20Hyderabad%20where%20they%20played%20two%20warm-up%20matches%20and%20will%20take%20on%20New%20Zealand%20on%20October%206%20in%20their%20tournament-opener.%20A%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20PTI%20reported%20that%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20has%20written%20to%20the%20ICC%20seeking%20prompt%20action%20on%20the%20visa%20process%20for%20its%20fans%20and%20media.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20hospitality%20was%20quite%20nice.%20We%20were%20not%20expecting%20this%2C%20but%20I%20think%20the%20way%20people%20are%20responding%20towards%20our%20team%2C%20everyone%20(has)%20enjoyed%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Babar%20told%20the%20media%20here%20during%20ICC's%20Captain's%20Day%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20(here%20since)%20a%20week%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20so%20it%20is%20not%20like%20we%20are%20in%20India%2C%20(but)%20it%20(feels)%20like%20we%20are%20(at)%20home.%20We%20are%20enjoying%20(it)%20and%20I%20think%20it%20is%20a%20golden%20opportunity%20for%20everyone%20to%20give%20their%20100%20per%20cent%20and%20enjoy%20the%20tournament%2C%26quot%3B%20Babar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBabar%20said%20it%20would%20have%20been%20nice%20to%20see%20fans%20from%20Pakistan%20among%20the%20Hyderabad%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20we%20came%20to%20Hyderabad%2C%20the%20hospitality%20we%20got%2C%20the%20way%20people%20welcomed%20us%2C%20from%20the%20airport%20to%20the%20hotel%2C%20the%20crowd%20in%20the%20ground%20and%20in%20the%20last%20match%2C%20we%20liked%20it%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20have%20been%20better%20if%20we%20had%20fans%20from%20our%20side.%20We%20will%20try%20to%20get%20such%20support%20in%20every%20match%2C%20in%20every%20stadium%2C%20in%20every%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20captain%20said%20despite%20the%20absence%20of%20right-arm%20fast%20bowler%20Naseem%20Shah%2C%20bowling%20remains%20his%20team's%20greatest%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20our%20strength%20is%20bowling.%20But%20as%20we%20know%2C%20we%20are%20playing%20(for%20the)%20last%20three%20years%20together.%20Most%20of%20the%20boys%20are%20the%20same.%20I%20think%20our%20strength%20is%20bowling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBabar%20said%20his%20squad%20was%20excited%20to%20play%20against%20India%20on%20October%2014%20here%20at%20the%20world's%20largest%20cricket%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20we%20are%20very%20excited%20because%20we%20have%20come%20here%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20the%2014th%20match%2C%20we%20have%20two%20matches.%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20go%20match-to-match%20and%20focus%20on%20each%20day.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20are%20excited%20about%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20as%20it%20is%20always%20a%20big%20match%2C%20so%20everyone%20is%20waiting%20for%20that%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20Babar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20many%20years%20since%20Pakistan%20players%20featured%20in%20the%20IPL%20as%20teams%20look%20to%20use%20their%20players'%20knowledge%20and%20understanding%20of%20the%20conditions%20going%20into%20the%20World%20Cup.%20Babar%20said%20Pakistan%20players%20are%20under%20no%20pressure%20in%20such%20a%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20is%20no%20pressure%2C%20the%20conditions%20here%20are%20similar%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20Asian%20conditions.%20It's%20been%20one%20week%20for%20us%20and%20we've%20played%20some%20practice%20and%20warm%20up%20matches%2C%20there%20is%20no%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20boundaries%20are%20small.%20There%20is%20no%20margin%20for%20the%20bowlers.%20If%20the%20bowler%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20off%2C%20the%20batsman%20utilises%20it.%20There%20will%20be%20high%20scores%2C%26quot%3B%20Babar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696511400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F2pia2r_a_625x300_04_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fit-is-not-like-we-are-in-india-babar-azam-bowled-over-by-fans-welcome-ahead-of-cricket-world-cup-2023-4450644%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20skipper%20Babar%20Azam%20said%20that%20he%20is%20completely%20feeling%20%26quot%3Bat%20home%26quot%3B%20in%20Hyderabad%20ahead%20of%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fit-is-not-like-we-are-in-india-babar-azam-bowled-over-by-fans-welcome-ahead-of-cricket-world-cu