20before%20Additional%20Sessions%20Judge%20Hardeep%20Kaur%20at%20the%20Patiala%20House%20Courts%20to%20be%20provided%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20FIR%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20court%20had%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcourt-notice-to-delhi-police-over-newsclick-founder-prabir-purkayastha-hr-heads-fir-copy-plea-101696415719857.html%5C%22%3Eissued%20notice%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20police%20on%20the%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20lawyers%20struggle%20to%20obtain%20the%20FIR%2C%20sections%20of%20the%20media%20seem%20to%20have%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fnewsclick-prabir-purkayastha-police-custody-8967869%2F%5C%22%3Eno%20problem%20in%20accessing%20the%20document%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20suggesting%20that%20the%20police%20force%20has%20chosen%20to%20selectively%20leak%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1057116%2Fwhy-is-newsclick-being-denied-fir-copy-even-as-it-is-leaked-to-the-media%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20accused%20has%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20be%20informed%20of%20the%20grounds%20under%20which%20they%20are%20arrested%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArticle%2022(1)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CNo%20person%20who%20is%20arrested%20shall%20be%20detained%20in%20custody%20without%20being%20informed%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20may%20be%2C%20of%20the%20grounds%20for%20such%20arrest%E2%80%9D.%20This%20is%20a%20near-absolute%20fundamental%20right%2C%20with%20extremely%20limited%20regulation%20imposed%20by%C2%A0Article%2022(3)%2C%20which%20is%20not%20applicable%20in%20the%20present%20case.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20lawyers%20have%20planned%20to%20challenge%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20FIR%20in%20court%2C%20but%20are%20being%20unable%20to%20do%20so%20without%20a%20copy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20against%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20its%20staff%20members%20and%20contributors%20has%20been%20criticised%20by%20media%20rights%20bodies%20across%20the%20country.%20Eighteen%20media%20organisations%20have%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmedia-organisations-write-chandrachud-freedom-press%5C%22%3Ewritten%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%3C%2Fa%3E%20expressing%20their%20alarm%20over%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20October%205%20at%203%3A05%20pm%2C%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20on%20the%20same%20date%20at%206%3A00%20pm%20with%20more%20updates.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696509083000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F09132731%2Fnewsclick.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdelhi-police-opposes-newsclick-editors-plea-for-copy-of-the-fir-under-which-he-is-arrested%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20the%20head%20of%20the%20portal's%20HR%20department%2C%20Amit%20Chakraborty%2C%20were%20arrested%20under%20the%20draconian%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20late%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A59%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdelhi-police-opposes-newsclick-editors-plea-for-copy-of-the-fir-under-which-he-is-arrested%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pics%20that%20prove%20Bhumi%20is%20the%20new%20glam%20gal%20in%20town%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696509000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104177096%2Cimgsize-70452.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fpics-that-prove-bhumi-pednekar-is-the-new-glam-gal-in-town%2Fphotostory%2F104177096.cms%2