English%20title%20is%20%3Cem%3EAnd%20We%E2%80%99ll%20Never%20Be%20Parted%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20was%20published%20in%201994%2C%20the%20prolific%20author%20went%20on%20to%20write%20some%2040%20theatrical%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20international%20breakthrough%20as%20a%20playwright%20came%20with%20the%201999%20staging%20of%20%3Cem%3ESomeone%20Is%20Going%20to%20Come%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20late%20French%20theatre%20director%20Claude%20Regy.%20The%20play%20centres%20on%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20who%20move%20to%20a%20run-down%20house%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere%20to%20be%20alone%2C%20but%20quickly%20become%20paranoid%20that%20%E2%80%9Csomeone%20is%20going%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20sparking%20hidden%20jealousies%20within%20the%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Booker%20Prize%20website%2C%20his%20plays%20have%20since%20been%20staged%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20times%20around%20the%20world%20in%2050%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFellow%20Norwegian%20author%20Karl%20Ove%20Knausgaard%2C%20who%20used%20to%20be%20his%20student%2C%20details%20how%20influential%20Fosse%E2%80%99s%20work%20was%20for%20him%20in%20%3Cem%3EMy%20Struggle%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20made%20Chevalier%20of%20the%20Ordre%20national%20du%20Merite%20of%20France%20in%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20one-sentence%20magnum%20opus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFosse%E2%80%99s%20magnum%20opus%20is%20his%20%3Cem%3ESeptology%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20published%20in%20three%20volumes%20from%202019-2021%20under%20the%20titles%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Other%20Name%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EI%20Is%20Another%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EA%20New%20Name%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThrough%20a%20single-sentence%20monologue%20of%20an%20elderly%20artist%20talking%20to%20himself%2C%20the%201%2C250-page%C2%A0prose%20work%20offers%20a%20bleak%20but%20ecstatic%20reflection%20on%20art%20and%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFosse%20has%20told%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Yorker%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine%20that%20the%2