that%20one%20Mr.%20Yadav%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20remember%20his%20name%2C%20is%20claiming%20to%20be%20my%20lawyer.%20I%20want%20to%20clarify%20that%20no%20one%20by%20that%20name%20is%20my%20lawyer%20and%20I%20have%20not%20signed%20any%20such%20Vakalatnama%20%5Ba%20document%20by%20which%20the%20party%20filing%20the%20case%20authorises%20the%20advocate%20to%20represent%20on%20their%20behalf%5D.%20This%20is%20absolutely%20untrue%20and%20fake%20news.%20There%20was%20some%20mention%20of%20Patiala%20House%20in%20one%20of%20the%20reports%E2%80%A6%20it%E2%80%99s%20absolute%20rubbish.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FMZojPazZSEw%3Fsi%3Dv4nEbZUcoblKvYQy%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20such%20a%20situation%20arises%20where%20I%20need%20legal%20assistance%2C%20then%20there%20are%20several%20eminent%20representatives%20in%20the%20country%20whom%20I%20and%20my%20well-wishers%20will%20contact%20and%20we%20will%20make%20sure%20we%20get%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696504799000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F11071727%2FUrmilesh.00_22_05_13.Still003.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnot-my-lawyer-urmilesh-rebuts-claims%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20senior%20journalist%20was%20questioned%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%20on%20October%203%20as%20part%20of%20raids%20on%20persons%20associated%20with%20NewsClick.%20He%20says%20neither%20he%20nor%20his%20family%20has%20hired%20any%20lawyer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnot-my-lawyer-urmilesh-rebu