%20winners%20P.%20Sainath%20and%20Aruna%20Roy%2C%20writers%20K.R.%20Meera%2C%20Perumal%20Murugan%2C%20Ramachandra%20Guha%20and%20V.%20Geetha%2C%20and%20singer%20T.M.%20Krishna%20have%20issued%20a%20statement%20condemning%20the%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20UAPA%20case%20and%20action%20against%20the%20editor%2C%20staff%20members%20and%20contributors%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20the%20undersigned%2C%20are%20deeply%20shocked%20and%20concerned%20about%20the%20arrest%20of%20two%20persons%20including%20the%20NewsClick%20editor%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20draconian%20UAPA%20and%20the%20blanket%20raids%20in%20the%20houses%20of%20about%2046%20newspersons%20associated%20with%20the%20NewsClick%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20October%203rd.%20This%20includes%20Githa%20Hariharan%2C%20Urmilesh%2C%20Aunindyo%20Chakravarti%2C%20Sohail%20Hashmi%2C%20Teesta%20Setalvad%2C%20Sanjay%20Rajoura%2C%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta%20and%20Anuradha%20Raman.%20All%20of%20them%20are%20well-known%20journalists%20and%20activists%20who%20have%20a%20commendable%20body%20of%20work%20to%20their%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20against%20NewsClick%20is%20a%20chilling%20attempt%20to%20silence%20their%20brave%20voices.%20Criticism%20is%20essential%20for%20a%20democracy%20and%20any%20attempt%20to%20mute%20voices%20is%20an%20assault%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20spirit.%20By%20foisting%20cases%20under%20sections%20of%20UAPA%20and%20sealing%20the%20office%20of%20NewsClick%20the%20State%20is%20attempting%20to%20vilify%20journalists%20who%20have%20consistently%20and%20fearlessly%20spoken%20truth%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20also%20come%20to%20know%20that%20many%20of%20them%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%2C%20and%20several%20of%20them%20have%20had%20their%20phones%20and%20laptops%20confiscated.%20This%20does%20not%20merely%20constitute%20a%20violation%20of%20their%20privacy%20but%20is%20also%20illegal%20since%20the%20devices%20have%20been%20confiscated%20without%20court%20orders%20and%20without%20their%20owners%20being%20informed%20of%20the%20details%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20record%20with%20concern%20that%20there%20have%20been%20reports%20in%20the%20past%20of%20manufactured%20%E2%80%98pieces%20of%20evidence%E2%80%99%20being%20planted%20in%20the%20confiscated%20devices%20of%20activists%20who%20were%20detained%20under%20UAPA.%20We%20are%20genuinely%20worried%20that%20similar%20attempts%20will%20be%20made%20in%20the%20case%20of%20journalists%20of%20NewsClick.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20urge%20stakeholders%20and%20concerned%20citizens%20to%20speak%20up%20against%20this%20harassment%20of%20NewsClick%20and%20its%20contributors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20dark%20moment%2C%20we%20record%20our%20deep%20appreciation%20of%20NewsClick%E2%80%99s%20stellar%20work%20in%20journalism%20and%20stand%20firmly%20in%20solidarity%20with%20all%20its%20staff%20and%20contributors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESignatories%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAruna%20Roy%3Cbr%3E%20Geetanjali%20Shree%3Cbr%3E%20K.R.%20Meera%3Cbr%3E%20P.%20Sainath%3Cbr%3E%20Perumal%20Murugan%3Cbr%3E%20Ramachandra%20Guha%3Cbr%3E%20T.M.%20Krishna%3Cbr%3E%20V.%20Geetha%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696503627000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05153723%2Fnewsclick-statement.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fstate-vilifying-journalists-who-speak-truth-to-power-renowned-writers-activists-on-newsclick-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20action%20against%20NewsClick%20is%20a%20chilling%20attempt%20to%20silence%20their%20brave%20voices.%20Criticism%20is%20essential%20for%20a%20democracy%20and%20any%20attempt%20to%20mute%20voices%20is%20an%20assault%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20spirit.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fstate-vilifying-journalists-who-speak-truth-to-power-renowned-writers-activists-on-newsclick-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bajaj%20Finance%20to%20raise%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20through%20QIP%2C%20preferential%20issue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696503173000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-07%2F27%2Ffull%2F1658917862-0655.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbajaj-finance-to-raise-rs-10-000-crore-through-qip-preferential-issue-123100500770_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20said%20it%20will%20raise%20up%20to%20Rs%208%2C800%20crore%20of%20capital%20through%20qualified%20institutional%20placement%20of%20shares%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbajaj-finance-to-raise-rs-10-000-crore-through-qip-preferential-issue-123100500770_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbajaj-finance-to-raise-rs-10-000-crore-through-qip-preferential-issue-123100500770_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbajaj-finance-to-raise-rs-10-000-crore-through-qip-preferential-issue-123100500770_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Activist%20Beena%20Johnson%20Becomes%20First%20Dalit%20Woman%20To%20Address%20UN%20General%20Assembly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05140521%2FF7gnrD6XUAAIng2.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EBeena%20Johnson%2C%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20National%20Campaign%20on%20Dalit%20Human%20Rights%20(NCDHR)%20became%20the%20first%20Dalit%20woman%20to%20address%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20on%20September%2018.%20She%20said%20that%20principles%20of%20non-discrimination%20should%20be%20upheld%20if%20poverty%20has%20to%20be%20eradicated%2C%20and%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20specific%20mechanisms%20to%20support%20women%20and%20transgender%20communities%20within%20the%20discriminated%20and%20vulnerable%20population.%20She%20was%20speaking%20during%20the%20second%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDG)%20Summit%20that%20was%20held%20in%20New%20York%20last%20month%20to%20review%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%202030%20Agenda%20for%20Sustainable%20Development%20and%20the%2017%20SDGs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20person%20belonging%20to%20the%20Dalit%20community%2C%20representing%20the%20stakeholder%20group%20on%20communities%20discriminated%20on%20work%20and%20dissent%2C%20including%20Dalits%2C%20Haratin%2C%20Roma%2C%20Killambola%2C%20and%20other%20people%20who%20are%20socially%20and%20economically%20excluded%20and%20discriminated%20intergenerationally.%20We%20number%20around%20270%20million%20across%20all%20continents%20together%20with%20the%20indigenous%20people%2C%20Afro-descendant%20people%2C%20people%20with%20disability%2C%20LGBTQIA%2B.%20Within%20these%20marginalised%20communities%20we%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20actually%20are%20the%20%E2%80%98leave%20no%20one%20behind%E2%80%99%20that%20the%20SDGs%20are%20currently%20focusing%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CLeave%20No%20One%20Behind%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20pledge%20of%20the%202030%20SDG%20that%20was%20adopted%20by%20members%20of%20the%20UN%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20overhaul%20the%20financial%20architecture%2C%20Beena%20put%20forth%20a%20multi-layered%20approach%20with%20which%20it%20should%20be%20done.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20we%20need%20to%20take%20into%20consideration%20the%20debt%20trap%20the%20southern%20nations%20are%20facing.%20This%20is%20a%20crime%20and%20we%20cannot%20allow%20a%20huge%20proportion%20of%20our%20budgets%20in%20many%20countries%20over%2050%25%20to%20be%20spent%20on%20debt%20servicing.%20This%20must%20be%20dealt%20with%20ruthlessly%20to%20ensure%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20massive%20debt%20relief%20strategy.%20There%E2%80%99s%20another%20layer%20which%20we%20normally%20ignore%20within%20the%20SDG%20mechanism%2C%20the%20intra-national%20fiscal%20infrastructure%20in%20both%20the%20northern%20and%20southern%20countries%20which%20are%20excluding%20socially%20marginalised%20from%20accessing%20the%20financial%20resources%20of%20the%20national%20budgets%20and%20wealth.%20This%20is%20equally%20critical.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20suggested%20six%20things%20that%20can%20be%20followed%20by%20the%20UN%20to%20achieve%20the%20SDG%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommunity%20engagement%3A%20involve%20the%20rights%20holder%20communities%20and%20decision-making%20processes%20regarding%20the%20allocation%20of%20funds%20and%20investments%20to%20ensure%20their%20needs%20and%20priorities%20are%20addressed%3B%20Targeted%20Budgeting%3A%20set%20portion%20of%20the%20nations%E2%80%99%20budget%20should%20be%20set%20aside%20to%20specially%20make%20them%20available%20to%20micro%20development%20of%20individuals%2C%20families%20and%20habitations%20where%20the%20socially%20excluded%20communities%20live.%20Some%20countries%20like%20India%2C%20Brazil%20and%20Mexico%20have%20adopted%20some%20of%20these%20significant%20steps%3B%20Socially%20responsible%20investment%20funds%3A%20promote%20the%20creation%20and%20growth%20of%20SRI%20%5BSocially%20Responsible%20Investment%5D%20funds%3B%20Inclusive%20financial%20services%3A%20local%20and%20community-based%20financing%2C%20international%20support%20engage%20with%20international%20organisations%20and%20donor%20agencies%20and%20development%20banks%20to%20mobilise%20financial%20resources%3B%20Engendering%20financial%20inclusion%3A%20we%20must%20also%20have%20specific%20mechanism%20to%20deal%20and%20to%20help%20support%20women%20and%20trans%20communities%20within%20these%20discriminated%20and%20vulnerable%20population.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20are%20serious%20about%20making%20poverty%20history%2C%20we%20must%20indulge%20in%20the%20principles%20of%20non%20discrimination%20and%20equitable%20resource%20mobilisation%20towards%20a%20resilient%2C%20inclusive%20and%20equitable%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fnews%2Factivist-beena-johnson-becomes-first-dalit-woman-to-address-un-general-assembly-2%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20in%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696501857000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05140521%2FF7gnrD6XUAAIng2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Factivist-beena-johnson-becomes-first-dalit-woman-to-address-un-general-assembly%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20National%20Campaign%20on%20Dalit%20Human%20Rights%20said%20that%20principles%20of%20non-discrimination%20should%20be%20upheld%20if%20poverty%20has%20to%20be%20eradicated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Factivist-beena-johnson-becomes-first-dalit-woman-to-address-un-general-assembly%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bail%20an%20Exception%2C%20Not%20a%20Rule%20in%20NDPS%2C%20UAPA%20Cases%3A%20Tripura%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F19195946%2FHC.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Tripura%20high%20court%20has%20said%20the%20general%20rule%20of%20%E2%80%98bail%20not%20jail%E2%80%99%20is%20not%20applicable%20to%20those%20accused%20in%20cases%20registered%20under%20the%20Narcotic%20Drugs%20and%20Psychotropic%20Substances%20Act%20(NDPS%20Act)%20and%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20NDPS%20Act%20cases%2C%20Justice%20Arindham%20Lodh%20observed%20that%20stringent%20provisions%20of%20the%20law%20make%20bail%20an%20exception%20rather%20than%20a%20rule%2C%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Ftripura-high-court-uapa-ndps-bail-exception-notrule%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20on%20a%20number%20of%20occasions%2C%20has%20highlighted%20that%20bail%20should%20be%20the%20rule%20and%20jail%20an%20exception%20to%20prevent%20%E2%80%9Cunnecessary%20arrests%E2%80%9D.%20The%20principle%20was%20first%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20apex%20court%20during%20the%20landmark%20judgment%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F8258%2F%5C%22%3EState%20of%20Rajasthan%20V.%20Balchand%20alias%20Baliay%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecase%20in%201978.%20Former%20judge%20V.R.%20Krishna%20Iyer%20had%20held%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20basic%20rule%20may%20perhaps%20be%20tersely%20put%20as%20bail%2C%20not%20jail.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Justice%20Lodh%20held%20that%20jail%20is%20the%20rule%20in%20the%20case%20of%20NDPS%20and%20UAPA%20cases.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6courts%20should%20not%20forget%20the%20rigours%20of%20NDPS%20and%20UAPA%20Act%20where%20it%20is%2C%20by%20now%20well%20settled%20that%20bail%20is%20not%20a%20rule%2C%20but%2C%20an%20exception%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Lodh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20took%20exception%20to%20lower%20courts%20dealing%20with%20NDPS%20cases%20%E2%80%9Cirresponsibly%20and%20rampantly%E2%80%9D%20granting%20bail%20to%20accused%20persons%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20procedural%20violations.%20He%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20procedural%20violations%20or%20irregularities%20should%20not%20be%20considered%20when%20deciding%20on%20bail%20pleas%20of%20those%20accused%20in%20NDPS%20and%20UAPA%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Lodh%20said%20granting%20bail%20in%20NDPS%20cases%20citing%20procedural%20issues%20amounts%20to%20a%20violation%20of%20Section%2037%20of%20the%20NDPS%20Act.%20The%20particular%20Section%20of%20the%20Act%20lays%20down%20limitations%20with%20regard%20to%20granting%20bail.%20The%20judge%20said%20procedural%20violations%20should%20be%20considered%20only%20during%20the%20trial%20stage%2C%20not%20at%20the%20bail%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%E2%80%99s%20observations%20were%20made%20during%20a%20hearing%20on%20the%20Tripura%20government%E2%80%99s%20plea%2C%20which%20sought%20cancellation%20of%20bail%20granted%20to%20three%20accused%20persons%20in%20an%20NDPS%20case.%20The%20government%20held%20that%20bail%20granted%20to%20the%20accused%20was%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20NDPS%20Act%2C%20while%20alleging%20that%20the%20accused%20were%20habitual%20offenders%20in%20the%20trade%20of%20illicit%20substances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLearned%20Special%20Judge%20did%20not%20consider%20at%20all%20the%20twin%20conditions%20as%20embodied%20in%20Section%2037%20of%20the%20NDPS%20Act%20and%20released%20the%20accused-respondents%20on%20bail%20on%20the%20erroneous%20conception%20that%20since%20there%20were%20procedural%20violations%2Firregularities%2C%20the%20accused%E2%80%93respondents%C2%A0were%20entitled%20to%20get%20the%20benefit%20of%20bail%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAllowing%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20appeal%2C%20the%20high%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20trial%20court%20had%20%E2%80%9Ctotally%20misdirected%20and%20misread%20the%20provisions%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Act%20in%20releasing%20the%20accused%20on%20bail.%20%C2%A0The%20court%20ordered%20two%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20out%20on%20bail%2C%20to%20surrender%20while%20the%20third%20accused%20is%20still%20in%20jail%20in%20relation%20to%20another%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696500037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F19195946%2FHC.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbail-an-exception-not-a-rule-in-ndps-uapa-cases-says-tripura-high-court%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'...courts%20should%20not%20forget%20the%20rigours%20of%20NDPS%20and%20UAPA%20Act%20where%20it%20is%2C%20by%20now%20well%20settled%20that%20bail%20is%20not%20a%20rule%2C%20but%2C%20an%20exception%2C'%20said%20Justice%20Arindham%20Lodh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbail-an-exception-not-a-rule-in-ndps-uapa-cases-says-tripura-high-court%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20extends%20tenure%20of%20SBI%20chairman%20Dinesh%20Khara%20until%20August%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696499877000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-07%2F20%2Ffull%2F1689851672-3236.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgovt-extends-tenure-of-sbi-chairman-dinesh-khara-until-august-2024-123100500653_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20is%20likely%20to%20issue%20an%20order%20to%20this%20effect%20shortly%2C%20the%20sources%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgovt-extends-tenure-of-sbi-chairman-dinesh-khara-until-august-2024-123100500653_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgovt-extends-tenure-of-sbi-chairman-dinesh-khara-until-august-2024-123100500653_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-stan