%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQZQVy1qNFFI%5C%22%3Epromotional%20material%3C%2Fa%3E%20used%20for%20these%20three%20series%20by%20Indian%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20then%20broadcast%20partner%20Star%20Sports%20was%20quite%20telling%2C%20though.%20It%20featured%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20but%20instead%20of%20exclusively%20leveraging%20their%20popularity%2C%20the%20ads%20served%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20role%20ODI%20cricket%20has%20specifically%20played%20in%20shaping%20their%20legacies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20statistical%20scale%20of%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%E2%80%99s%20batting%20records%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20unforgettable%20double%20hundreds%2C%20or%20Virat%20Kohli%E2%80%99s%20astounding%20exploits%20while%20chasing%20totals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ads%20took%20no%20subtle%20measures%20in%20reminding%20fans%20that%20it%20is%20the%20nature%20and%20design%20of%20ODI%20cricket%20that%20allowed%20for%20some%20of%20their%20greatest%20living%20memories%20to%20be%20formed.%20It%20was%20as%20close%20as%20the%20broadcasters%20could%E2%80%99ve%20come%20to%20admitting%20the%20ODI%20format%20itself%20has%20considerably%20slipped%20out%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20watching%20habits.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20obviously%20all%20the%20more%20concerning%20in%20a%20World%20Cup%20year%20as%20the%20quadrennial%20occasion%20still%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20flagship%20event%20this%20sport%20has%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResetting%20the%20fans%E2%80%99%20viewing%20preferences%20therefore%20was%20absolutely%20paramount%20and%20it%20further%20showed%20when%20the%20ICC%20themselves%20ensured%20their%20campaign%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20too%20repeatedly%20headlined%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eone-day%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20takes%20one%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20certain%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20kept%20saying%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yo