r%20started%20writing%20charters%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20in%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20women%20behind%20the%20victory%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20582px)%20100vw%2C%20582px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbill4-1695994589.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22582%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pramila%20Dandavate%20at%20a%20meeting%20discussing%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbill4-1695994589.jpg%20582w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbill4-1695994589-300x220.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbill4-1695994589-500x366.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbill4-1695994589-150x110.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331342%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22426%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPramila%20Dandavate%20at%20a%20meeting%20discussing%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20bill.%20Image%20courtesy%20CSR%20India%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201987%2C%20former%20prime%20minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20constituted%20a%20committee%20for%20the%20National%20Perspective%20Plan%20for%20Women.%20This%20committee%20was%20led%20by%20union%20minister%20Margaret%20Alva%20and%20proposed%20reservations%20in%20rural%20and%20local%20body%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20was%20drafted%20by%20this%20committee%20of%20women%20parliamentarians%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Alva%2C%20Geeta%20Mukherjee%2C%20Susheela%20Gopalan%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F214827%2Fvalentines-day-love-letters-emergency-madhu-pramila-dandavate-history-nor41%2F%5C%